  credit       = {The project was conceived jointly by myself, Ackerly, and Goodbred. The bulk of this paper focused on geological measurements and analysis designed and conducted by Auerbach, Goodbred, Mondal, and Wilson. I contributed synthesis between the geological and social sciences, made with land-use in other parts of the delta, and did historical research on the evolution of scientific thinking about sediment dynamics and flood control in Bengal since the 19th century.},
